# =============================================================================
# .dockerignore - Excluye del build context lo que no necesita Docker.
# Reduce el tamaño del context (acelera builds) y evita que secretos o
# artefactos locales acaben dentro de las imagenes.
# =============================================================================

# --- Dependencias instaladas ---
**/node_modules
.pnpm-store

# --- Builds previos (cada Dockerfile los regenera dentro del builder) ---
**/dist
**/build
**/.next
**/out
**/.turbo
**/*.tsbuildinfo

# --- Prisma generated client (se regenera en el builder) ---
**/.prisma
**/node_modules/.prisma
packages/database/node_modules/.prisma

# --- Git / VCS ---
.git
.gitignore
.gitattributes
.github

# --- Variables de entorno (NUNCA dentro de la imagen) ---
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# --- Logs ---
**/*.log
**/logs

# --- Tests ---
**/coverage
**/.nyc_output
**/test
**/__tests__
**/*.spec.ts
**/*.test.ts

# --- IDE / OS ---
.vscode
.idea
**/.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
*.swo

# --- Docker / Compose ---
Dockerfile*
docker-compose*.yml
.dockerignore

# --- Documentación ---
docs
*.md
!README.md

# --- Husky / lint-staged (no se ejecutan dentro del contenedor) ---
.husky
lint-staged.config.mjs

# --- Backups y scripts host-only ---
scripts/backups
backups
